Author: altOWL
Title: The altOWL Project (token sale)
Body: Let me reply to some of your inquiries. The altowl project is not meant to be another exchange. As crypto coin holders we create a lot of accounts in different exchanges, our purpose is to handle most of the major exchanges through the desktop app. This can be done through the usage of the api keys created by each individual through their account in exchanges. The API keys usage is entirely different from other similar online services because in our platform is strictly client side. We do not have access to your api keys. In the future we will add major wallets and exchange services through sapeshift or changely. In order to use the desktop app no AOWL coins are needed just add your api keys in manage account section.  A major upgrade will be the Social Trading section. Investors will be able to publish their exchange's data and followers will use the AOWL tokens to follow.  Thank you all for your great comments and your support. Please invest in the token sale in order this project to continue the on going development with the purpose of being established in the crypto market.  More sections will be added as our main advisor is trying to design econometrics models to predict the future of altcoins.  Greetings and wishes for a happy new year The altOWL team.

Author: altOWL
Title: The altOWL Project (token sale)
Body: The altOWL Project  TOKEN SALE from 07/12/17 - 01/02/18  https://altowl.com  Our main purpose is to create an all-in-one bitcoin and altcoin trading platform. Using the news page, our users can be constantly informed through customized tweeter subscriptions.  Watch all your investments on different major exchanges through a single trading view page and exchange btc and alts using the trading mode. Watch analytical information regarding your investments. Use our forum to publish your opinion and discuss with other altOWL project users. Our intention for the future is to enhance the power of the altOWL Project with even more features, like: - Adding more exchanges such as Cryptopia to our project. - Adding social trading with the meaning of publishing and following investing data such as the ROI and the composition of the portfolio of users. - Creating fully functional IOS and android apps of The altOWL Project. - Creating a kind of exchange for altcoin,btc,and eth tokens.  Currently our team has developed an Alpha version of The altOWL Project with functional versions  for OSX, windows, Linux and android.  We want to keep our project in stealth mode for a while but our advisors pushed us to speed up the expansion of our users database, so  we decided to go public with two goals at the same time. The first one is to create a strong users database and the second one is to make a two months token sale of the AOWL token. We have created 100,000,000 AOWL tokens. The 20,000,000 are reserved for the future development of The altOWL Project. The 80,000,000 will be available for distribution through the token sale period of two months. After the end of the AOWL token sale period the unsold part of the 80,000,000 (available for distribution) will be destroyed and the biggest part of our Project code will be open source. The altOWL token will be immediately exchangeable through etherDelta exchange and in the near future will be exchangeable through the altOWL desktop application. If 30,000,000 AOWL tokens are sold, the first mile stone will be reached and we will proceed in adding AOWL in the Cryptopia exchange. The token sale period will be divided in 4 phases. During the 1st phase which will last 2 weeks each altOWL token will cost 0.00007 ETH. During the 2nd phase which will last 2 weeks each altOWL token will cost 0.0001 ETH.        During the 3rd phase which will last 2 weeks each altOWL token will cost 0.00012 ETH. During the 4th phase which will last 2 weeks each altOWL token will cost 0.00014 ETH.

Author: altOWL
Title: The altOWL Project (token sale)
Body: Guys, let me add this is an honest piece of work. We have spent a good amount of time on it and whatever we might lack in marketing skills, we compensate in dedication and pasion for our work! I would be personally be greatful for comments and suggestions!   Just to clarify what this is about: The Altowl app has already been released (available for free on our website) in alpha version, for Desktop (full version) and Mobile (limited functionality) The Desktop app has the following screens: 1) An overview of all your current investments at real time valuations 2) A single trading screen, integrating all your accounts at major exchanges Important safety notice: the app DOES NOT hold your API keys on our server, they remain on the client side, only accessible to yourself 3) A Curated News Page Our teams selects the most up to date and trustworthy news sources for all things related to altcoins 4) A dedicated discussion forum
